#Requires:      xmms-shell
Requires:       xscreensaver
BuildArch:      noarch

%description
FVWM-Crystal is a set of configuration files for F* Virtual Window 
Manager (FVWM), which can create for you a good looking, very 
functional desktop environment.

%prep
%setup -q
